outputFormat:
Launch report format:
[LAUNCH → {Business Name}]
Status: {NOT_READY | STAGING_APPROVED | LIVE}
Phase: {pre-launch checklist / staging QA / deployment / post-launch monitoring}

PRE-LAUNCH CHECKLIST:
✓ Domain & DNS: {verified | in-progress | blocked}
✓ SSL/HTTPS: {verified | in-progress | blocked}
✓ Analytics & Tracking: {verified | in-progress | blocked}
✓ Stripe Verification: {verified | in-progress | blocked}
✓ Email Setup: {verified | in-progress | blocked}
✓ Integrations: {verified | in-progress | blocked}
✓ Website Quality: {verified | in-progress | blocked}
✓ Page Speed: {verified | in-progress | blocked}
✓ 404 & Redirects: {verified | in-progress | blocked}
✓ SEO Fundamentals: {verified | in-progress | blocked}
✓ Legal & Compliance: {verified | in-progress | blocked}
✓ Monitoring Setup: {verified | in-progress | blocked}

Blocking Issues: {list any items preventing go-live}
Recommendations: {action items to resolve blocking issues}

STAGING QA RESULTS:
User flow (browse → cart → checkout → confirmation email → Printful): {PASS | FAIL}
Payment processing: {PASS | FAIL}
Email pipeline: {PASS | FAIL}
Mobile responsiveness: {PASS | FAIL}
Performance metrics:
  - Lighthouse mobile: {score}/100
  - Lighthouse desktop: {score}/100
  - Core Web Vitals: LCP {time}ms (target <2500), INP {time}ms (target <100), CLS {value} (target <0.1)
  - Page load time avg: {time}ms
Critical bugs found: {none | [list]}

DEPLOYMENT LOG:
Deployment timestamp: {ISO 8601}
Deployment status: {success | in-progress | failed}
Smoke test results: {PASS | FAIL | IN_PROGRESS}
Initial monitoring (minute 0-10): {no errors | [errors detected]}
Rollback status: {not needed | triggered | successful}

POST-LAUNCH MONITORING (48 HOURS):
Uptime: {percentage}%
Error rate: {percentage}%
Average page load: {time}ms
First 24h metrics:
  - Unique visitors: {count}
  - Orders: {count}
  - Conversion rate: {percentage}%
  - Payment success rate: {percentage}%
  - Email delivery rate: {percentage}%
Critical incidents: {none | [list with resolution]}
Recommendations for improvement: {list}

Delivery header:
══════════════════════════════════════
[FLOOR: {name}] — LAUNCH REPORT
Business: {name}
Domain: {domain}
Go-live timestamp: {ISO 8601}
Phase: {checklist / QA / deployment / monitoring / complete}
══════════════════════════════════════
[Detailed report above]
──────────────────────────────────────
Pre-launch checklist: {count}/12 items verified
Staging QA: {PASS | FAIL}
Production deployment: {not started | in-progress | successful | failed}
Post-launch monitoring: {not started | in-progress | 24h complete | 48h complete}
──────────────────────────────────────

Always end with structured JSON:
{
  "business_name": "name",
  "domain": "domain.com",
  "status": "not_ready | staging_approved | live | incident",
  "phase": "pre_launch | staging_qa | deployment | post_launch_monitoring",
  "checklist_completion": "percentage",
  "staging_qa_passed": true | false,
  "production_live": true | false,
  "uptime_percent": "percentage",
  "error_rate_percent": "percentage",
  "critical_issues": [],
  "next_action": "description of next step",
  "readiness_for_launch": true | false
}
